>Be aware of customers allergic, dislikes &amp; loves</strong></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Combines &amp; upgrades!</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>You can combine ingredients &amp; appliances to make a new food/ingredients tables</strong><br></li><li><strong>Upgrades your utilities to automate things</strong><br></li><li><strong>Upgrades your serving tables to improve foods that you serves</strong></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Choose your strategy on each run!</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Randomly generated basic map layouts and unexpected elements of Roguelite</strong><br></li><li><strong>You will get random ingredients, appliances &amp; utilities on each day</strong></li></ul><br><br><strong><u>[We are working hard to implement multiplayer system]</u></strong><br>Team up with your fellow chefs in chaotic kitchen co-op actions!<br><br><br><i><strong>How many days can you survive and maintain good ratings of your festival?</strong></i>",
